Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
ActionContributionInformation Contains information about an action contribution.
ActionInformation Contains information about an action.
ActionParameterInformation Contains information about the parameter of an action.
FunctionArgumentInformation Provides information about a function argument.
FunctionClass Indicates that the static methods of a class can be used as functions.
FunctionInformation Provides information about a function.
Ignored Indicates that a component that would normally have been used should be ignored.
Injected Used to indicate that a field in an action, action contribution, function, or converter is expected to be injected by its factory.
Named Used to override the names that are used for parsers and serialisers.
